    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The primary validation result demonstrates RH prediction accuracy within ±12% across all five COU operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
